<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<graphml xmlns="http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/xmlns" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/xmlns http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/xmlns/1.0/graphml.xsd">
  <key id="d6" for="edge" attr.name="order" attr.type="long" />
  <key id="d5" for="edge" attr.name="source_id" attr.type="string" />
  <key id="d4" for="edge" attr.name="description" attr.type="string" />
  <key id="d3" for="edge" attr.name="weight" attr.type="double" />
  <key id="d2" for="node" attr.name="source_id" attr.type="string" />
  <key id="d1" for="node" attr.name="description" attr.type="string" />
  <key id="d0" for="node" attr.name="entity_type" attr.type="string" />
  <graph edgedefault="undirected">
    <node id="&quot;IMAGE_17&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The image displays a small, low-resolution, pixelated icon set against a solid black background. The icon itself is rendered in shades of white and light gray, creating a stark contrast. It depicts a simplified, front-facing representation of what appears to be a vehicle, possibly a bus, van, or trailer. The main body of the vehicle is a horizontal rectangle, slightly wider than it is tall. Within this larger rectangle, two smaller, squarish or rectangular shapes are centrally placed, side-by-side, which could represent windows or headlights. Below the main body, a small, dark, circular or oval shape is visible, suggesting a wheel or a hitch point. The overall design is highly stylized and abstract, typical of a pictogram or symbol, lacking fine details due to its limited resolution."</data>
      <data key="d2">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_17.jpg</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;VEHICLE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A highly pixelated, white silhouette of a generic vehicle, possibly a car, bus, or van, viewed from the side. It has a boxy shape with two distinct rectangular areas that could represent windows. The vehicle is depicted as a simple icon or sprite."</data>
      <data key="d2">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_17.jpg</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BACKGROUND&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A solid, uniform black background that provides strong contrast for the white pixelated vehicle. It appears to be a void or a simple dark canvas."</data>
      <data key="d2">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_17.jpg</data>
    </node>
    <edge source="&quot;IMAGE_17&quot;" target="&quot;VEHICLE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">10.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Vehicle是从image_17中提取的实体。"</data>
      <data key="d5">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_17.jpg</data>
      <data key="d6">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;IMAGE_17&quot;" target="&quot;BACKGROUND&quot;">
      <data key="d3">10.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Background是从image_17中提取的实体。"</data>
      <data key="d5">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_17.jpg</data>
      <data key="d6">1</data>
    </edge>
  </graph>
</graphml>
